data.description: Welcome to 6323 18th Street!!   This home is a MUST SEE!!!  Please come enjoy the  brightly lit entry way that compliments the mahogany wood floors  and recessed lighting, throughout first floor.  This open concept leads to a spacious eat-in kitchen with  ceramic tile floor,  stainless steel appliances and beautiful granite counters, accented back splash and wood  cabinets.  The lovely wooden staircase leads to three  spacious bedrooms with nice size closets,  a  bathroom with a gorgeous ceramic tiles shower and stylish fixtures  and vanity.    The  fully finished amazing basement  with a beautifully modern style bathroom,  clean and bright laundry area , land walkway to a rear entrance.  The driveway and garage provide no issues with parking.  The  rear steel stairs  provide  straight access to kitchen,    The central air will keep you comfortable throughout the hot summers.   The home is close to schools, transportation, parks and shopping  centers.     This AMAZING home  is ready for your family!!!!
